{"type":"message","id":"1fc42425","parentId":"f4955afa","timestamp":"2026-03-07T02:23:01.892Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Still `-2`! This is incredibly persistent. The gateway (pid 6530) is STILL using `memory-dir-main-2`. \n\nOK, I think I fundamentally misunderstand how OpenClaw resolves collection names. Let me look more carefully.The gateway starts and resolves collection names. Even though `memory-dir-main` wasn't in QMD when the gateway started, the gateway still creates `memory-dir-main-2`. This suggests the `existing` set in `ensureUniqueName` is NOT populated from QMD, but from something else — perhaps from the `index.yml` file directly, or from a persisted state.\n\n\nWait - actually, looking at `qmd collection list` output: it shows `memory-dir-main` with 13 files \"Updated: 42m ago\". This means qmd already had `memory-dir-main` in its state before the gateway started. So when the gateway calls `qmd collection add` for `memory-dir-main`, it must be detecting that the collection already exists and creating a numbered variant instead.\n\nOh, I see what's happening now. The tool definitions get locked in when the session initializes - so this current session has `memory-dir-main-2` baked into its configuration. A fresh session would resolve to the correct `memory-dir-main` collection. The solution is straightforward: the user needs to start a new session with `/new` or `/reset` to pick up the right collection name.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Still `-2`. I now understand the root cause — the collection name is baked into **this session's tool definitions** when the session started, not resolved on each call. No amount of gateway restarts will fix it mid-session.\n\n**The fix is simple: start a new session.** Hit `/new` or `/reset` and the fresh session will pick up `memory-dir-main` correctly. QMD itself is healthy — this is purely a session initialization artifact from when things were misconfigured."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":626,"cacheRead":54105,"cacheWrite":187,"totalTokens":54919,"cost":{"input":0.000003,"output":0.00939,"cacheRead":0.0162315,"cacheWrite":0.00070125,"total":0.026325750000000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772850167473}}
